name: Panty pull / Panty drop
description:
*Added a slightly refined v2 version purely focusing on "pantypull".

This is a first iteration of a LoRA model trained on a couple hundred photos, that provides a concept in two flavors:

-Pantypull: Pulling down panties with one or both hands

-Pantydrop: Panties dropped down somewhere along the legs without hands involved.

*It still has some quirks, most notably double panties and it often not quite making the distinction between pull and drop when prompted.

I'm looking to expand on these concepts and make them more varied/consistent. While it's almost purely trained on front-facing poses, it can do some generations from the rear as well.

Many thanks to brandnewfakeuser for making the amazing Shirtlift LoRA and also including his training parameters, which are similar to what I have used for this LoRA.

The example images were generated using QGO-10b-fix model.

Additional LoRA used in the examples:

-Shirtlift: https://civitai.com/models/6693/shirtlift-a-lora-for-flashing-tits

-That's my bush!: https://civitai.com/models/6946/thats-my-bush
